! Nord Theme for CodeMirror 6

An arctic, bluish color palette based on [[Nord|https://www.nordtheme.com/]].

Clean, minimal, and elegant with a dark polar night and bright snow storm variant.

!! Variants

* `nord` / `nord-dark` - Dark polar night theme (default)
* `nord-light` - Light snow storm variant

!! Usage

Add the theme class to your editor container or set the `data-cm6-theme` attribute:

```html
<div class="cm6-theme-nord">
  <!-- editor here -->
</div>
```

Or via attribute:

```html
<div data-cm6-theme="nord-light">
  <!-- editor here -->
</div>
```

!! Available Theme Classes

| !Class | !Description |
| `cm6-theme-nord` | Dark Nord theme (Polar Night) |
| `cm6-theme-nord-dark` | Same as above |
| `cm6-theme-nord-light` | Light Nord theme (Snow Storm) |
